data.title: Todd Goodwin
data.meta_description: Todd Goodwin is a highly experienced project manager here at Design Collaborative, with many years in the A/E/C industry.
data.text:
Project Manager,

Todd Goodwin, a project manager here at Design Collaborative, enjoys engaging in the project management process and providing sharing management lessons, concepts, and practices that he has acquired over the many years of service in the architectural and construction industry. He is an excellent resource and mentor for the staff and community with his knowledge of the A/E/C industry. Todd appreciates the warm culture here at DC.

In his free time, Todd relaxes by gardening, cooking, taking on home renovation projects, and fishing. In his earlier years, Todd boxed for Summit City in Fort Wayne!
